name: True color image of impact zones D and G
description:
This true color image of the giant planet Jupiter, by NASA and ESA's Hubble Space Telescope, reveals the impact sites of fragments 'D' and 'G' from Comet Shoemaker-Levy 9.

Name:	Jupiter, Shoemaker-Levy 9
